    "Similarly, Gao et al.",
    "43 studied the impact of financial Twitter sentiment on Bitcoin returns and high-frequency volatility.",
    "Their findings showed a significant link between Twitter sentiment and Bitcoin returns, with positive sentiment leading to higher returns and negative sentiment leading to lower returns.",
